title: Episode 155: Luke Tyburski - The Ultimate Triathlete
description:
Show Notes:
Luke Tyburski is a former professional footballer (soccer) player turned triathlete and voted in the 50 of the worlds fittest athletes in 2016. He has a fascinating story about having to retire from football due to injury and getting into endurance sports to follow and the life lessons that came along the way.
